title: Lynda - Up and Running with Google Photos
description:
Lynda - Up and Running with Google Photos 
36m 48s Beginner Jun 01, 2015 | Uploaded in Aug 25, 2015 Via Webcentara

Subjects:Business Photography 
Software: Photos 
Author: Nick Brazzi 

Get off to a great start with Google Photos. In this course, Nick Brazzi provides a quick overview of the essential features of Google's free cloud-based photo storage service. He shows how to set up Google Photos on iOS, Android, and desktop computers and then how to organize, edit, and share photos and videos.
